text: Mpumelelo Xulu (born 28 January 1999) is a South African cricketer. He made his List A debut for KwaZulu-Natal Inland in the 2018–19 CSA Provincial One- Day Challenge on 17 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:KwaZulu-Natal Inland cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
